{"tid":402153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海洋公園「哈囉喂」添亡魂，男子鬼屋傷頭不治","createTime":"2017-09-16T08:00:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T12:12:23.000Z","uid":29314,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"8c2f7f64fa07dfd043fdf29928690722beec4410","tid":402153,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:00:27.000Z","msg":"海洋公園「哈囉喂全日祭」今午發生命案。下午2時許，一名20多歲男子在香港仔海洋公園意外受傷昏迷，救護員接報到場將他送院，經搶救後證實不治，警方正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，死者一行七人趁海洋公園舉辦「哈囉喂全日祭」入場，其間他與另外兩名友人在鬼屋「活埋凶間」遊玩時，意外跌傷頭部昏迷，送院不治。"},{"pid":"b508e12ee568451fd2200a0f80ac662a4d71cf39","tid":402153,"uid":22349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:02:56.000Z","msg":"蘋果個標題：<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/160255_35f6cc230b7ae085f52b6424f731bea8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F160255_35f6cc230b7ae085f52b6424f731bea8.jpg&h=d9d7978d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8ad2017fc8bd33f3c53dcfe71194c47171ae0be","tid":402153,"uid":47296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:05:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76fe43142cddc21df5a287e58d1b48a01dec566b","tid":402153,"uid":3180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:05:53.000Z","msg":"搵替身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92a14c405264e2bed7e2b5945b07d06e27d22f69","tid":402153,"uid":45693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:05:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a92addac17de9e5eb0d2362672e9d7e72744eb12","tid":402153,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:08:15.000Z","msg":"現場消息指，死者一行七人趁海洋公園舉辦「哈囉喂全日祭」入場，其間他與另外兩名友人在鬼屋「活埋凶間」遊玩時，意外跌傷頭部昏迷，送院不治。<br />\n鬼屋恐慌之最首推一人遊戲《活埋凶間》，在《活埋凶間》需要孤身上路。場景以歐洲中世紀巫毒的活埋生葬為題，遊人將各自躺在一個棺木內，並分別滑落至下層迷宮內。各人均會被滑落至不同的位置作為起點，然後在四通八達的並佈滿嘩鬼及機關的迷宮內尋找出口，可能會在途中與友人重逢，或需要獨自走完全程，並有可能被困良久，未能找到出口。"},{"pid":"0fe69055c4404be888199075ef743aab91ce20eb","tid":402153,"uid":22349,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:10:37.000Z","msg":"會唔會唔知自己死咗，以為自己仲玩緊？"},{"pid":"aaf96af6d02b414d2f30c9e621afa39e1a1cc362","tid":402153,"uid":22507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:11:42.000Z","msg":"真係要瞓棺木<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4b21878c3221bb192cdb3ba96454c441810203b","tid":402153,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:11:56.000Z","msg":"總算有d 恐怖野。<br />\n如果個場無封的話。"},{"pid":"a00b0b7f1c5a80f5671e87586dc6faa48d47a975","tid":402153,"uid":71315,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:12:20.000Z","msg":"抵撚死"},{"pid":"6b77db195c17c119ce68a342dd16d7b4e6c25ba3","tid":402153,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:12:55.000Z","msg":"嘩...邊有人仲敢入去玩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw RIP"},{"pid":"8af64c8a05140f5598bded7a976352b5986d2d09","tid":402153,"uid":127123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:13:36.000Z","msg":"真係有鬼既鬼屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82aa26b0743fdff4dcda3f59f08773100368cf80","tid":402153,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:13:57.000Z","msg":"變真鬼屋"},{"pid":"d8d740e650b75e62ff8d3b0642d9af53bfb7a7f5","tid":402153,"uid":33293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:45:22.000Z","msg":"真係生葬"},{"pid":"770255e6916b6b3371a1c0f992f8c89c4826371d","tid":402153,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-